Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Who Shall Police the Policemen?
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00sq03p
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 6 Jun 2003
Alistair Cooke asks how we can police the world in a time of modern terrorist conflict since America's founding fathers never legislated for an "undeclared" war.